      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in immaculate, showroom-quality condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, has been maintained to an uncompromising standard. This is an exemplary specimen for the sophisticated buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. We invite you to experience a vehicle that transcends the typical pre-owned market through its peerless mechanical and aesthetic state.",
