    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows in every detail. It drives like a total dream and is just waiting for someone new to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
