      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it\u2019s truly a gem. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for an adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
