      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in mechanical preservation. Under the hood, the S54 straight-six remains a high-revving marvel, featuring a documented Double VANOS overhaul and verified rod bearing service. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers surgical precision with crisp synchro engagement, delivering linear power through a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has been meticulously maintained, including a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings to preserve the original suspension kinematics. With a flawless exterior and an interior showing zero bolster wear, this example provides the tactile feedback and visceral intake note that defined the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance.",
